[SN]TITLE[SN]
Tom Hunter on EU referendum: 'Where are the facts?'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Scottish entrepreneur and philanthropist Sir Tom Hunter is still undecided how he will vote in the EU referendum.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
6 May 2016 Last updated at 03:28 BST
He says he is worried about the UK's sovereignty within the EU, but would be concerned about trade if the UK left.
My Decision is a series of films by BBC Newsnight in which a number of well-known figures explain how they plan to vote, and the thinking behind their decision.
